effect_entries.effect:
This Pokmon's Speed is doubled during strong sunlight.

This bonus does not count as a stat modifier.

effect_entries.short_effect: Strengthens grass moves to inflict 1.5 damage at 1/3 max HP or less.
effect_entries.effect: When this Pokmon has 1/3 or less of its HP remaining, its grass-type moves inflict 1.5 as much regular damage.
